# Testing Standards

## Coverage Requirements

Minimum coverage requirements:
- Statements: 80%
- Branches: 75%
- Functions: 80%
- Lines: 80%

Excluded paths:
- src/types/**
- **/*.d.ts

## Test Types

### Unit Tests
- Pattern: **/*.unit.test.js
- Location: tests/unit
- Naming: <feature>.unit.test.js

### Integration Tests
- Pattern: **/*.integration.test.js
- Location: tests/integration
- Naming: <feature>.integration.test.js

### E2E Tests
- Pattern: **/*.e2e.test.js
- Location: tests/e2e
- Naming: <feature>.e2e.test.js

## Conventions

### Structure
- Group related tests in describe blocks
- Use clear test descriptions
- Follow AAA pattern (Arrange-Act-Assert)

### Naming
- Test descriptions should be explicit
- Use 'should' in test descriptions
- Describe expected behavior 